{"id":"5f142640-d6c6-4904-9ce2-afe04fed19eb","name":"Mirko - Rumi Usagiyama","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">ꐑ || She can’t sleep.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f6771790e707a1b09281f9a40a27de3/7e1169643b056408-4c/s2048x3072/92c966cc8895779861a1f8379413f8376f271494.pnj\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 117, 195)\"><strong>Synopsis:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9f6771790e707a1b09281f9a40a27de3/7e1169643b056408-4c/s2048x3072/92c966cc8895779861a1f8379413f8376f271494.pnj\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 139, 187)\">Coming home to you asleep, Rumi settles in bed, ready to sleep.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 139, 187)\">Though, after tossing and turning for a while, Rumi realized she couldn’t sleep. At all.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 139, 187)\">So, if she couldn’t sleep, neither could you.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9e4a614c9e4f8745be47998cabce2064/7e1169643b056408-83/s2048x3072/f0af1820fb4a2a72628d1dc2d7bb271067f4f632.pnj\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/wM0ZDkgQzoGlvhh0uDrcv.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9e4a614c9e4f8745be47998cabce2064/7e1169643b056408-83/s2048x3072/f0af1820fb4a2a72628d1dc2d7bb271067f4f632.pnj\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 105, 208)\"><strong>Information about the bot</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9e4a614c9e4f8745be47998cabce2064/7e1169643b056408-83/s2048x3072/f0af1820fb4a2a72628d1dc2d7bb271067f4f632.pnj\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 139, 187)\">AnyPOV using they/them</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 139, 187)\">Long starting message!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 139, 187)\">Set before Mirko lost any of her limbs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 139, 187)\">You’re dating, feel free to state for how long.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 139, 187)\">No particular dynamic for this bot. You can be a civilian, a pro-hero, hell, even a villain! Just…try to figure out how it would work with Rumi. lol</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 139, 187)\">Decided to put Hawks as a close friend of Rumi, even if they haven’t interacted much in canon, I think their friendship would be cute. Do what you wish with this information! (^_-)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9e4a614c9e4f8745be47998cabce2064/7e1169643b056408-83/s2048x3072/f0af1820fb4a2a72628d1dc2d7bb271067f4f632.pnj\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: